<h1> Welcome to VaiLocal! </h1>

<h3>VaiLocal is a hyper-local jobs board and social network for high school and college students. Apart from listing jobs on our site, we also seek to connect high schoolers who have questions about college, internships, scholarships, athletics recruiting, and more on a forum with college students who can offer guidance. </h3>

<h2>Create your account today!</h2>

